1.title: Episode #3.1

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

1.plot: Scarlett, Joel and Joe discuss the campmates' arrival with Andi Peters and Megan McKenna, plus behind-the-scenes with the production crew, pre-jungle chats with the contestants, Keith Lemon on the phone, and Harry in the Bush Telegraph.

2.title: Episode #3.2

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

2.plot: Emily's victory in the first Bushtucker Trial, "The Viper Pit", is discussed with Megan McKenna and Andi Peters, Holly and Dec play "Willoughby, Wallaby, Wobbly", plus Fleur is live in the Bush Telegraph.

3.title: Episode #3.3

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

3.plot: Anne's failure in the second Bushtucker Trial, "Monstrous Monoliths", is discussed with Megan and Andi, Critters Ben and Colette the Python are live in the studio, Holly and Dec play "Land Down Under", plus Nick is in the Bush Telegraph.

4.title: Episode #3.4

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

4.plot: John's success in the third Bushtucker Trial, "Scary Rose", is discussed with Andi and Olivia, news on Noel's arrival, Holly and Dec play "Donnelly, Dingoey, Dollopy", Medic Bob is live in the studio, Megan competes in the first Main Camp vs. Extra Camp trial, plus James is in the Bush Telegraph.

5.title: Episode #3.5

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

5.plot: Noel's arrival for the fourth Bushtucker Trial is discussed with Olivia Attwood and Dean Gaffney, an exclusive pre-Jungle interview with Noel, plus Joe goes behind-the-scenes of the the show's biggest ever set-build, the colosseum.

6.title: Episode #3.6

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

6.plot: Rita and Malique's success in the fifth Bushtucker Trial, "Drown and Out", is discussed with Olivia Attwood and Dean Gaffney, as well as the care package terracotta challenge, Holly and Dec play "Eel or No Eel", the first set of KNOBS questions, plus Emily is live in the Bush Telegraph.

7.title: Episode #3.7

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

7.plot: Noel and Harry's success in the sixth Bushtucker Trial, "Nero to Zero", is discussed with Olivia Attwood and Dean Gaffney, Holly and Dec play "Jungle Jinx", Harry's granddaughter is live on the phone, the Big Camp Quiz of the Week, Joe and Olivia compete in the second Main Camp vs. Extra Camp trial, plus Malique is live in the Bush Telegraph.

8.title: Episode #3.8

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

8.plot: Noel and Nick's failure in the seventh Bushtucker Trial, "Catch a Falling Star", as well as the campmates' success in the eighth trial, "The Jungle X Factor", is discussed with Dean Gaffney and Lady Leshurr, Nick's son is live on the phone, Joe and Dean compete in the third Main Camp vs. Extra Camp trial, plus A Quickie with Sair.

9.title: Episode #3.9

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

9.plot: James, John and Rita's success in the ninth Bushtucker Trial, "The Quest", is discussed with Lady Leshurr and Sam Thompson, Holly and Dec play another round of "Willoughby, Wallaby, Wobbly", the week's top I'm a Celeb Google searches, A Quickie with Fleur, plus John is live in the Bush Telegraph.

10.title: Episode #3.10

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

10.plot: Anne's triumph in the tenth Bushtucker Trial, "Hellish Hospital", is discussed with Lady Leshurr and Sam Thompson, Holly and Dec play "24 Seconds in A&E", Owen Warner is live on the phone, Critters Ben and Graham the Crocodile are live in the studio, Leshurr competes in the fourth Main Camp vs. Extra Camp trial, A Quickie with Nick, plus Rita is live in the Bush Telegraph.

11.title: Episode #3.11

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

11.plot: Sair and Malique's triumph in the eleventh Bushtucker Trial, "Dreaded Deliveries", is discussed with Sam Thompson and Stanley Johnson, Holly and Dec play "Get in the Calzone", Tisha Merry is live on the phone, Joe and Sam compete in the fifth Main Camp vs. Extra Camp trial, A Quickie with James, plus Noel is live in the Bush Telegraph.

12.title: Episode #3.12

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

12.plot: The first set of Immunity Games challenges are discussed with Stanley Johnson and Alison Hammond, Holly and Dec play the deciding round of "Willoughby, Wallaby, Wobbly", the second set of KNOBS questions, Duncan James from Blue is live on the phone, Swashy takes on the Critters, plus Anne is live in the Bush Telegraph.

13.title: Episode #3.13

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

13.plot: Joe interviews Noel, the first campmate to be voted off, the second set of Immunity Games challenges are discussed with Stanley Johnson and Alison Hammond, the campmates' family and friends are live in the studio to dish the dirt, A Quickie with Harry, Joe and Alison compete for the title of Best Roving Reporter, plus Fleur is live in the Bush Telegraph.

14.title: Episode #3.14

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

14.plot: Sair's triumph in the twelfth Bushtucker Trial, "Sickening Sewers", is discussed with Alison Hammond and Kem Cetinay, Noel is live in the studio, this week's top I'm a Celebrity Google searches, Joe goes behind-the-scenes with the Challenge Team, A Quickie with Emily, plus James is live in the Bush Telegraph.

15.title: Episode #3.15

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

15.plot: Joe interviews Malique, the second campmate to be voted off, Fleur's triumph in the thirteenth Bushtucker Trial, "Gore Seasons Pizza", is discussed with Alison Hammond and Kem Cetinay, Christopher Biggins is live on the phone, Joe goes behind-the-scenes of the Pizza trial, plus, it's the Big Camp Quiz of the Week.

16.title: Episode #3.16

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

16.plot: Joe interviews Sair, the third campmate to be voted off, Rita and James' success in the fourteenth Bushtucker Trial, "Stars of the Silver Scream", is discussed with Kem Cetinay and Toff, Malique is live in the studio, Joe and Scarlett compete in the sixth Main Camp vs. Extra Camp trial, Jamie Redknapp and The Speakmans are live on the phone, plus John is live in the Bush Telegraph.

17.title: Episode #3.17

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

17.plot: Joe interviews Rita, the fourth campmate to be voted off, Harry, Nick and Fleur's success in the fifteenth Bushtucker Trial, "Wicked Warehouse", is discussed with Kem Cetinay and Toff, Sair is live in the studio, the third set of KNOBS questions, A Quickie with John, plus Emily is live in the Bush Telegraph.

18.title: Episode #3.18

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

18.plot: Joe interviews Anne, the fifth campmate to be voted off, John and Fleur's success in the sixteenth Bushtucker Trial, "Rotten Retrieval", is discussed with Toff, Rita is live in the studio, Joel performs "Extra Camp: The Musical", Joe meets the campmates' friends and family, Joe and Toff compete in the seventh Main Camp vs. Extra Camp trial, plus Harry is live in the Bush Telegraph.

19.title: Episode #3.19

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

19.plot: Joe interviews Nick, the sixth campmate to be voted off, James and Fleur's success in the seventeenth Bushtucker Trial, "Ding Dong Merrily Up High", is discussed with Noel, Anne is live in the studio, Joe and Joel compete in the eighth Main Camp vs. Extra Camp trial, plus it's the Extra Camp Jungle Awards.

20.title: Episode #3.20

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

20.plot: Joe interviews James, the seventh campmate to be voted off, Harry's success in the eighteenth Bushtucker Trial, "Repvile Centre", is discussed with Sair, Nick is live in the studio, Scarlett chats to the friends and family of this year's final four, a celebration of Joe's ten years of chaos, plus a sneak peek at this year's Celebrity Cyclone.

21.title: Episode #3.21

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

21.plot: Joe interviews Fleur, the eighth campmate to be voted off, Rita and James are live in the studio, Joe, Scarlett, Holly and Joel compete in the ninth Main Camp vs. Extra Camp trial, it's the Big Camp Quiz of the Series, plus all three finalists are live in the Bush Telegraph.

22.title: Episode #3.22

episode of.title: I'm a Celebrity... Extra Camp (TV Series 2016– )

22.plot: The three finalists, Harry, Emily and John, join the rest of their Class of 2018 campmates live in the studio for this year's series finale at the Extra Camp Coronation Disco, plus Holly and Dec play a final game of "Willoughby, Wallaby, Wobbly".
